{"tid":1216621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港人講地 我屌你老母","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:16:48.000Z","uid":202849,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53777f073a144f2bbfc893dab647043323b70867","tid":1216621,"uid":202849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"到底係乜撚嘢垃圾page黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEVTDBh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEVTDBh.png&h=2852784a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQVMd9D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQVMd9D.png&h=509de790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痴鳩線係咪有撚病？點解咁嘅說話都可以講得出口？<br />\n仲難聽過粗口<br />\n之後入去睇吓 全部post都係警察有幾慘 咩青少年俾人利用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9ne7vH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9ne7vH.png&h=61881ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n挑釁警方？？？？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解唔講啲狗點吠呀？？<br />\n記你老母 自由閪去撚咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣唔係挑釁係乜呀 講啲唔講啲</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBB7H5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBB7H5d.png&h=9e90f4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHO2wYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHO2wYz.png&h=850ad94d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72RvFRV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72RvFRV.png&h=1b83b2a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bzt2wYA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzt2wYA.png&h=704676d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最撚仆街係居然有人附和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到咁真係好心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地班青年就出黎為香港去抗爭 <br />\n傷左咁多人 流左咁多血 <br />\n班人都可以冇感覺 <br />\n呢個真係我熟悉嘅香港黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c04f28980647d8517bdf5eb2956a3d752b2492","tid":1216621,"uid":191815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"港人港地不嬲五毛集中地"},{"pid":"f82af04e5881b360066855a1bea1a44e77851e93","tid":1216621,"uid":39127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"又陳浚成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4d56088fb57780bfa33c69ca5165f5bce026c3","tid":1216621,"uid":111006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"佢地圍爐理閪佢地啦<br />\n牆ge出面全世界都屌緊政府同黑警"},{"pid":"afc1f36a47115b280dc9957c242149f5b04c78eb","tid":1216621,"uid":227026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"一齊檢舉個page"},{"pid":"379f4b2ad884562efbaab3c9e1d9aeae9e9bffd0","tid":1216621,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c249c5453e04e9083beb1a1fba0e0eb7db5fad","tid":1216621,"uid":78907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"個乜撚嘢尹智宏權係軟飯狗？點解個名咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7026451eceb1daf81108c304c837aadfe8ba9f54","tid":1216621,"uid":202849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f82af0